short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds web service integrations for MediaMod

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension support for SoundCloud, YouTube Music and other services in MediaMod for Minecraft!
The extension currently supports the following services:

- SoundCloud
- Apple Music
- YouTube
- YouTube Music
- Google Play Music

When you start using the extension, when you're on one of the supported services you will instantly get the player inside of Minecraft showing what's playing from all of these websites! It's simple and easy to use with not much to do to setup! If you wish to disable it but keep it installed you can do it from the mod.

Requires MediaMod to work!
